    <h3 class="text-center"><span><strong>OUR MISSION</strong></span></h3>
    <p>
      <span id="logo-font"><strong>Heartful.ly</strong></span> celebrates lifeâ€™s most important moments by connecting couples and their communities to locally-driven infrastructure and development projects around the world through a charitable gift registry platform. With its unique, personalized take on crowdfunding, Heartful.ly transforms weddings into vehicles for positive social change. 
